name: Bitcoin Surges Past $106K on Shutdown Optimism
description: The bio-mechanical saint kneels only to discharge fate, forcing the dense code sphere to tear through the volumetric ceiling of teal fog. Iridescent coolant streams as tungsten light bleeds incandescent cyan-magenta, ripping open the systemic lattice in a ritual surge of kinetic rebirth.
